(Choraku-ji Temple) Later on, all Zenke shrines except for {{ill|Ukishima Shrine and Yomochi Shrine#Ukishima Shrine|ja|世持神社|lt=Choju Shrine|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Choraku-ji Tenmangū|en}} would convert to {{ill|Shingon Buddhism|ja|真言宗|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and become the {{ill|Eight Ryukyu Shrines|en}}.
